= Sinatra's Hat

Mount models as web services in Sinatra with ease.

== Your Code

  %w(rubygems dm-core dm-serializer sinatra sinatras-hat).each { |lib| require lib }

  class Post
    include DataMapper::Resource
    include DataMapper::Serializer
    property :id, Serial, :key => true
    property :name, String
  end
  
  configure do
    DataMapper.setup(:default, 'sqlite3::memory:')
    Post.auto_migrate!
    Post.create :name => 'A test', :body => "Some sort of thing"
  end
  
  mount(Post)

== Usage

  $ ruby example/app.rb &
  $ curl http://localhost:4567/posts.json
  $ curl http://localhost:4567/posts/1.json
  $ curl http://localhost:4567/posts/1.xml

